                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts123" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts124">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ē. w bayyanaw ǧābāw xayām, gāmat tiǧi ʕād at-taxātre w-ᵊb-hawāde b-hawāde b-hawāde b-hawāde gāmat ʕād tiǧi tinkatt taxātre.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
